983 WGPUTextureUsage_RenderAttachment = 0x00000010,
984 WGPUTextureUsage_TransientAttachment = 0x00000020,
985 WGPUTextureUsage_StorageAttachment = 0x00000040,
986 WGPUTextureUsage_Force32 = 0x7FFFFFFF
987} WGPUTextureUsage WGPU_ENUM_ATTRIBUTE;
